@ description: Comprehensive example covering every OWF 4.0 feature for Isopepe parity
@ author: Test Suite

# Leg Day [Strength Training] (2026-04-01)
@ location: Downtown Gym

> High-volume quad focus. Ensure full recovery from last squat session.
> If gym is busy, substitute Hack Squat for Leg Press.

- Back Squat 3x8rep @100kg @tempo 3010 @rest 2min
- Back Squat 1x5rep @60kg @warmup @rest 90s
- Leg Extension 3x12rep @40kg @drop @rest 30s
- Pull-Up 3xmaxrep @failure @rest 2min
- Hack Squat 4x6rep @80kg @cluster @rest 20s
- Bench Press 1x12rep @60kg @rest-pause @rest 15s
- Leg Press 1x20rep @150kg @myo-rep @rest 20s
- Plank 3x60s @rest 30s

# Threshold Ride [Cycling] (2026-04-01)

> Stay in Z1-Z2 for warmup and cooldown. Push hard on intervals.

- Warmup 10min @Z1:power
- Bike 40min @Z2:hr
- Bike 3x5min @88%LTHR @rest 2min
- 3x:
  - Bike 10min @95%FTP
  - Recover 5min @Z1:power
- Cooldown 10min @Z1:power

# Pool Session [Swimming] (2026-04-01)

> Focus on consistent splits. Use paddles for the 200m sets.

- Swim 400m @Z1
- 4x:
  - Swim 100m @1:32/100m @Z3:pace
  - Recover 50m @Z1
- 2x:
  - Swim 200m @Z3:pace
  - Recover 100m @Z1
- Swim 200m @Z1

# Rowing Intervals [Rowing] (2026-04-01)

> Damper setting 5. Focus on drive sequence: legs-back-arms.

- Warmup 5min @Z1
- Row 4x500m @1:45/500m @rest 90s
- Cooldown 5min @Z1

# Evening Run [Running] (2026-04-01)

> Easy pace with a tempo block in the middle.

- Warmup 10min @Z1
- Run 20min @92%maxHR
- Run 3km @90%TP
- Run 5km @4:30/km
- Cooldown 10min @Z1

# Strength Finisher [Strength Training] (2026-04-01)

> Quick superset and circuit to close out the day.

- Bench Press 3x5rep @85%1RM @tempo 31X0 @rest 2min
- superset 3x:
  - Dumbbell Row 10rep @32kg @rest 60s
  - Incline Dumbbell Bench Press 10rep @28kg @rest 60s
- circuit 4x:
  @ rest_between_rounds: 90s
  - Kettlebell Swing 15rep @24kg
  - Push-Up 15rep
  - Goblet Squat 12rep @24kg
  - Pull-Up 8rep
  - Burpee 10rep

# CrossFit WOD [HIIT] (2026-04-01) @RPE 9

> Scale as needed. Time cap is firm.

- for-time 15min:
  - 5x:
    - Deadlift 12rep @70kg
    - Hang Clean 9rep @70kg
    - Push Jerk 6rep @70kg

# EMOM Session [HIIT] (2026-04-01)

> Pacing: each movement should take 30-40s max.

- every 1min for 12min:
  - Deadlift 5rep @100kg
  - Strict Press 7rep @40kg
  - Toes-To-Bar 10rep

# AMRAP Finisher [HIIT] (2026-04-01)

> Target: 20+ rounds.

- amrap 20min:
  - Pull-Up 5rep
  - Push-Up 10rep
  - Air Squat 15rep
